Review Palmetto's User Guide if you are unfamiliar with Palmetto before continuing.
http://citi.clemson.edu/palmetto/pages/userguide.html

To compile on palmetto: 
	# module add gcc/4.4 mpich2/1.4 fftw/3.2.2-double cuda-toolkit/5.0.35
	# make
	(Updates to palmetto will regularly break this.  See the module section of the Palmetto user guide)
To run on palmetto:
	# 